      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 16:29:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>零售交易员不断耕种美国股票，但速度正在放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/retail-traders-keep-plowing-into-us-stocks-but-pace-is-slowing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[个人投资者在周五将现金投入到他们最喜欢的股票中，并在交易所交易的资金中投下，押注美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战触发的市场抛售将在长远来看会带来购买机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/retail-traders-keep-plowing-into-us-stocks-but-pace-is-slowing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 16:25:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储的鲍威尔：觉得我们不需要着急</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/fed-s-powell-feels-like-we-don-t-need-to-be-in-a-hurry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）表示，感觉中央银行有时间对利率进行所需的调整，因为“目前尚不清楚货币政策的适当途径。”鲍威尔（Powell）周五在推进商业编辑和写作年度会议学会上发表了讲话。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/fed-s-powell-feels-like-we-don-t-need-to-be-in-a-hurry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 16:21:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球衰退担心吞噬华尔街的关税报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在金融市场的每个角落，从股票到债券再到商品，投资者都向唐纳德·特朗普传达了同样的信息：他释放的贸易战争威胁要引发全球衰退＆mdash;和快速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔信号仍被搁置，警惕持续的价格冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/powell-signals-fed-would-respond-to-persistent-inflation-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）表示，新关税的经济影响可能会大大比预期的要大得多，并且中央银行必须确保这不会导致通货膨胀越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/powell-signals-fed-would-respond-to-persistent-inflation-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂停鸡肉，高粱从一些美国公司进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-suspends-chicken-sorghum-imports-from-some-us-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统宣布对亚洲国家的新关税之后，中国暂停了从两名美国生产商进口的鸡肉进口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-suspends-chicken-sorghum-imports-from-some-us-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，越南愿意消除对美国商品的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，林的越南领导人愿意取消关税，以免惩罚对东南亚国家进口的新美国职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当鲍威尔信号损坏关税时，股票下沉：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储董事长杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）表示，贸易战争的损害将比预期的要大，股票加深，债券飙升和石油的股票飙升和石油跌至四年低点，其潜在影响包括更高的通货膨胀和较慢的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
